                                                </p>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="tab_icons">
                                                <div class="icon">
                                                    <span class="fas fa-bed"></span>
                                                    <p class="icon-bottom">
                                                        FACTORY
                                                    </p>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="icon">
                                                    <span class="fas fa-glass-martini"></span>
                                                    <p class="icon-bottom">
